{"tid":574481,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[港澳台次簽] 香港土長球員羅素加盟中甲球隊遼寧宏運","createTime":"2018-02-27T12:16:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-28T11:13:47.000Z","uid":9030,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"07b79acc632161ca5c4052e8d17b44014f336b36","tid":574481,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T12:16:51.000Z","msg":"和富大埔中堅羅素將加盟中甲球隊遼寧宏運。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/02/27/EBafWY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F02%2F27%2FEBafWY.jpg&h=aded06fa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f985051fde828c78e4126122f137e96a72bc5362","tid":574481,"uid":20105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T12:21:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43b5711fd236fa6b267750bcfcbf4c742291cdc8","tid":574481,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T12:23:37.000Z","msg":"羅素生於英國修咸頓，於18個月大時隨父母移居香港，直到18歲時返回祖家英國曼徹斯特繼續學業，到2008年畢業後返港與當時仍在甲組聯賽角逐的老牌球會愉園簽下首份職業球員合約。<br />\n<br />\n球季完結後再度重返英格蘭更加盟英格蘭北部超級聯賽球會摩士利，其後再在2010年轉會英格蘭全國北聯賽球會喬利，到2013年加盟同一聯賽球會菲爾德。<br />\n<br />\n2014年7月，羅素獲港超聯傳統球會南華賞識邀請加盟，而因他童年時已在港居滿七年，所以可以本地球員身份註冊本地賽事。<br />\n<br />\n2017年1月，羅素獲馬來西亞超級聯賽球會檳城垂青，惟加盟後因傷患問題令表現未如理想，5月9日檳城與羅素達成解約協議提前解約回復自由身。<br />\n<br />\n2017年7月16日，羅素回流加盟港超聯地區球會和富大埔。<br />\n<br />\n2018年2月27日，因中國足協介定羅素能以港澳台球員身份注冊，遼寧宏運正式簽入羅素。"},{"pid":"2a3ad892950991d86dce58a42c4ac376ef386e9a","tid":574481,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T12:24:11.000Z","msg":"傳羅素月薪接近30萬人民幣"},{"pid":"67e5e024a9d3be549a48e3bc86c1de5ed16dc56f","tid":574481,"uid":14983,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T12:31:57.000Z","msg":"血統撚: 唔喺香港出世+鬼佬樣<br />\n佢唔係香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f48820a12ff767f327d7cf5c7cc7c6f1a197f8f7","tid":574481,"uid":14983,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T12:34:34.000Z","msg":"認真佢嘅effort真係值得哩個回報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4dc95df959c778f70beaac046d031e241342c11","tid":574481,"uid":9030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f48820a12ff767f327d7cf5c7cc7c6f1a197f8f7","tid":574481,"uid":14983,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T12:34:34.000Z","msg":"認真佢嘅effort真係值得哩個回報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T12:43:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c17219765ec7113e963db07d3d67605badde7598","tid":574481,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T07:40:30.000Z","msg":"遼寧宏運剛正式公佈羅素加盟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/28/154026_1b86bd68c1437592e597d4b23919b463.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F28%2F154026_1b86bd68c1437592e597d4b23919b463.jpeg&h=98afccfc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b09285d1aee1e75d2a61a00376b3022723996da4","tid":574481,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T07:40:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/28/154054_e3440634de053222a5e4c6097ebba04b.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F28%2F154054_e3440634de053222a5e4c6097ebba04b.jpeg&h=5e79ce1c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eaead7f4f5c9bcda832b40581a58bc0aaa8d0475","tid":574481,"uid":27605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T07:52:25.000Z","msg":"細個睇愉園有睇佢 唔識踢咁 <br />\n要卓卓carry<br />\n轉下眼就踢中超啦"},{"pid":"0beb4f7917e9dfe7a67c4493ceaa4c2fe12a78e2","tid":574481,"uid":27605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eaead7f4f5c9bcda832b40581a58bc0aaa8d0475","tid":574481,"uid":27605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018